&lt;p&gt;📍 &lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Portland, OR | 🏥 &lt;strong&gt;Site Name:&lt;/strong&gt; Summit Research | 🕒 &lt;strong&gt;Full-Time&lt;/strong&gt; | 🧪 &lt;strong&gt;Clinical Research&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Clinical Research Assistant (RA)&lt;/strong&gt; for our clinical research site located in downtown Portland. As an RA, you won’t just be supporting research—you’ll be helping shape the future of healthcare. This is an exciting opportunity for individuals with clinical experience who are ready to grow their skillset and income potential within the clinical research field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;💼 The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
